__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT "District" AS "District",
       class AS class, 
       "Performance",
       "Q1_Performance",
       "Q2_Performance",
       "Q3_Performance",
       "Q4_Performance",
       "Q5_Performance",
       "Q6_Performance",
       "Q7_Performance",
       "Q8_Performance",
       "Q9_Performance",
       "Q10_Performance",
       "Q11_Performance",
       "Q12_Performance",
       "Q13_Performance",
       "Q14_Performance",
       "Q15_Performance",
       "Q16_Performance",
       "Q17_Performance",
       "Q18_Performance",
       "Q19_Performance",
       "Q20_Performance"
FROM
  (SELECT "District",
          CAST("class" AS STRING) AS "class",
          (CAST(Total_Score AS FLOAT) / CAST(max_score AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q1 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q1_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q2 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q2_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q3 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q3_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q4 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q4_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q5 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q5_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q6 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q6_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q7 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q7_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q8 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q8_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q9 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q9_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q10 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q10_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q11 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q11_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q12 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q12_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q13 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q13_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q14 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q14_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q15 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q15_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q16 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q16_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q17 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q17_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q18 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q18_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q19 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q19_Performance,
          (CAST(Total_Q20 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q20_Performance
   FROM
     (SELECT "District",
             "class",
             sum(Total) as "Total_Score",
             count(*) * 20 as "max_score",
             count(*) as "child_count",
             sum("Q1") as "Total_Q1",
             sum("Q2") as "Total_Q2",
             sum("Q3") as "Total_Q3",
             sum("Q4") as "Total_Q4",
             sum("Q5") as "Total_Q5",
             sum("Q6") as "Total_Q6",
             sum("Q7") as "Total_Q7",
             sum("Q8") as "Total_Q8",
             sum("Q9") as "Total_Q9",
             sum("Q10") as "Total_Q10",
             sum("Q11") as "Total_Q11",
             sum("Q12") as "Total_Q12",
             sum("Q13") as "Total_Q13",
             sum("Q14") as "Total_Q14",
             sum("Q15") as "Total_Q15",
             sum("Q16") as "Total_Q16",
             sum("Q17") as "Total_Q17",
             sum("Q18") as "Total_Q18",
             sum("Q19") as "Total_Q19",
             sum("Q20") as "Total_Q20"
      FROM classes
      GROUP BY "District",
               "class") AS A) AS expr_qry
GROUP BY "District",
         class
ORDER BY "Performance" DESC
select "District", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )")) As Gender, AVG(Total) As perf from classes GROUP BY "District", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )"))
